{"ANFRACTUOSE":[{"def":"Anfractuous; as, anfractuose anthers.","pos":""}],"ANFRACTUOSITY":[{"def":"A sinuous depression or sulcus like those separating the convolutions of the brain.","pos":""}],"ANFRACTUOUS":[{"def":"Winding; full of windings and turnings; sinuous; tortuous; as, the anfractuous spires of a born.","pos":""}]}